      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior is flawless with no scratches, dings, or paint imperfections. The interior is in like-new condition with no signs of wear on the upholstery, dashboard, or carpets. All systems and features are fully functional and show no signs of use.",
